Football fans on DStv and GOtv are in for treat! Ahead of the tournament which kicks-off on Friday, 11th June 2021, DStv and GOtv customers can relive some of the most classic Euro matches from 1972 to 2016, watch UEFA Euro official stories which includes documentaries from the 1960 tournament to the 2008 event, get entertained with ‘Road To Euro 2020’ an official magazine show, witness amazing memories of the greatest European players to have played the beautiful game and other UEFA Euro Archives programming.Here are a few Pre-Euro 2020 activities to look forward to:      For more pre Euro 2020 activities, visit www.superSport.com. Customers can reconnect their account to watch Pre-Euro moments on all DStv packages starting from N2,565p/m or GOtv JOLLI package for only N2,460 p/m. Visit www.dstvafrica.com and www.gotvafrica.com to subscribe or upgrade your DStv and GOtv packages for the Euro 2020 experience. With the DStv Explora, you can pause, rewind or record the exciting moments of the matches. And while you’re on the move, stream matches on the DStv App which is free for download on the Apple and Google Play store and can be used on up to 5 devices